57
00:05:19,977 --> 00:05:24,998
And possibly I would suggest moving this, I think, into a subcommittee at this point.

58
00:05:25,078 --> 00:05:29,600
I understand we're already in committee of the whole, but I think it may have been moved to a committee of the whole prematurely.

59
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:36,181
