172
00:15:52,525 --> 00:15:55,627
Uh, Tom Lincoln, uh, 27, uh, Gleason street.

173
00:15:56,316 --> 00:15:59,477
I've been following this process the best I can.

174
00:16:00,957 --> 00:16:03,538
And I know it's been a long road here.

175
00:16:04,278 --> 00:16:05,178
