180
00:16:50,332 --> 00:17:18,626
The other thing I wanted to raise, wearing another hat here, is that the committee that's been working on the comprehensive plan, if you've looked at the draft there, this is a very high priority item in the draft plan, great public concern about trees, the shade canopy, it's related to issues of open space protection, both on public and private property in Medford.

181
00:17:18,806 --> 00:17:19,527
And I think that,

182
00:17:20,933 --> 00:17:21,874
it would be very good.

183
00:17:22,674 --> 00:17:35,600
