191
00:18:45,576 --> 00:18:47,277
I think this is a goal.

192
00:18:47,838 --> 00:18:59,384
an environmental goal and a climate goal, a mitigation goal, an aesthetic goal for the city and its residents that needs to be met on a whole number of fronts.

193
00:18:59,564 --> 00:19:01,585
And there are lots of places for trees.

194
00:19:02,025 --> 00:19:06,987
There's lots of places where we can do more, we can do better.

195
00:19:07,007 --> 00:19:15,472
We're not going to solve this issue next week or next year, but it's a matter of what the trend is.

196
00:19:17,477 --> 00:19:22,598
