00:32:19,433 --> 00:32:28,997
Medford residents with trees giving shade to their house's roof, who decided to remove those trees to install solar panels, may not be able to pay the huge removal tax, and as a result, desist from going solar.

326
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:34,223
The electricity not produced by those rooftop panels will need to be produced somewhere else.

327
00:32:34,824 --> 00:32:43,411
Placing an electricity generation far away from electricity consumers can lead to clearing forests and largest bodies of trees with even greater adverse environmental impacts.

328
00:32:43,795 --> 00:32:45,576
than cutting a few trees in cities.

329
00:32:46,997 --> 00:32:55,801
I should mention that I did send a link to document with citations for all of this to all the city councilors and anyone that would like it, I will be happy to send it.

