00:32:57,602 --> 00:33:03,626
So Medford should launch a massive educational campaign to teach residents about the diverse positive impacts of trees.

332
00:33:04,266 --> 00:33:09,749
This go beyond increasing resilience to climate change, supporting wildlife and improving the aesthetics of places.

333
00:33:10,229 --> 00:33:13,371
