335
00:33:20,768 --> 00:33:31,176
In conclusion, the proposed MET for tree ordinance encroaches too far on the rights of individual landowners by imposing a tree removal tax on residents owning their house and living in it.

336
00:33:33,273 --> 00:33:50,027
