00:43:53,302 --> 00:43:57,765
And I think that if we regulate arborists, we'll be doing the same thing.

427
00:43:57,845 --> 00:44:06,631
Homeowners won't be unaware cutting down trees illegally because the arborists won't be allowed to do that and wouldn't do that.

428
00:44:07,551 --> 00:44:08,272
Thank you very much.

